<!-- Entitlements for FREE personal signing teams, which Apple does not allow
     to hold the Hotspot Configuration capability. Built with this file, the
     app cannot join the Bridge Wi-Fi programmatically; onboarding falls back
     to the manual-join screen (join in iOS Settings, then continue).
     Paid teams should build with the default InstantLink.entitlements. -->
